From: davidme@qdpii.ind.dpi.qld.gov.au (David Meiklejohn)
Subject: Well done, Commodore!
Message-ID: <CG7s94.E34@qdpii.ind.dpi.qld.gov.au>
Organization: Queensland Dept of Primary Industries
